headline: Strength Seen in Hillman Solutions Corp. (HLMN): Can Its 6.4% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Hillman Solutions Corp. (HLMN) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
